        <Parent_String>intermediate varnish [300014979], varnish by function [300014976], varnish [300014974], coating by composition or origin [300014908], coating (material) [300014907], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
